item.title: Day 5 of Vancouver Trip
item.description: On day 5 of my trip to Vancouver, I visited Sea to Sky Gondola. During this adventure I took A Gondola 885 meters above sea level to Vancovers famous mountains. When I reached the mountains I saw a more broad view of the mountains

item.title: Day 4 of Vancouver Trip - Part 2
item.description: After I went the the Butchart Gardens, I went to see some other sceneic lookouts. The first one I saw was called Highrock park.

item.title: Day 4 of Vancouver Trip - Butchart Gardens
item.description: Day 4 of my trip started off at the Butchart Gardens. The Butchart Gardens is an 118 year old garden that was created 1904.

item.title: Day 3 of Vancouver Trip
item.description: On day 3, I took a ferry to Victoria, the capital of British Columbia. The ferry trip was about 1-2 hours.

item.title: Day 2 of Vancouver Trip
item.description: On day 2 of my trip, I took a cruse ship and saw the many parks and places Vancouver had. During the cruse trip I saw factories, parks, cargo ships and more.

item.title: Day 1 of Vancouver Trip
item.description: The first day of my trip to Vancouver was super exiting. I first took a flight from Ontario to Vancouver and landed in Vancouver at around 11:00 PST.
